<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:fillViewport="true">
    <LinearLayout
        android:orientation="vertical"
        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
        android:layout_height="fill_parent">

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/t_1"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text="華富邨（Wah Fu Estate）"
            android:textSize="30dp"
            android:background="@drawable/shape"/>



        <ImageView
            android:id="@+id/hk_1"
            android:src="@drawable/hk4"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="200dp"
            android:background="#FF9900"
            android:scaleType="fitXY"
            android:layout_below="@id/t_1"
            android:layout_marginTop="30dp"
            />
        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/t2"
            android:layout_width="fill_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:text=" 華富邨（Wah Fu Estate）位於南區西部瀑布灣畔，是老牌公共屋邨，也是全港首個以新市鎮形式規劃的公共房屋。華興樓及華昌樓是香港首批落成的雙塔式大廈，有別了從前的中央走廊式及露台相連式大廈。
Wah Fu Estate is located in the western part of the Southern District, and is a veteran public housing estate. It is also the first public housing in Hong Kong to be planned in the form of a new town. Wah Hing House and Wah Cheong House are the first two-tower buildings in Hong Kong. They are different from the former central corridor and terrace-connected buildings.

" android:textSize="20sp" />
        <Button
            android:id="@+id/view"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="60dp"
            android:layout_below="@id/t2"
            android:background="@drawable/shape"
            android:text="更多資訊 More Information"
            android:textSize="20dp"/>
        <Button
            android:id="@+id/loc1"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="60dp"
            android:layout_below="@id/view"
            android:background="@drawable/shape"
            android:text="路線"
            android:textSize="50dp"/>


    </LinearLayout>

</ScrollView>